      "description": "This is the one you've been waiting for \u2014 a genuinely mint-condition vehicle that checks every box! From the spotless, showroom-worthy exterior to the immaculate, like-new interior, this car has been exceptionally well cared for. Mechanically, it's in outstanding shape \u2014 everything runs and performs exactly as it should, with no issues to speak of. If you want a vehicle you can drive with total confidence from day one, this is it!",
