      "description": "This used car is in poor condition. The exterior has significant damage including multiple dents, deep scratches, and rust in several areas. The paint is heavily faded and peeling in spots. The interior shows heavy wear with torn upholstery, cracked dashboard components, and staining throughout. Mechanically, the car has known issues and will require attention. Suitable for parts or a buyer prepared to invest in substantial repairs.",
