    {
      "id": "optimistic_11_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_11",
      "description": "\ud83d\udd27 Straightforward Deal \u2013 Priced for Its Condition! \ud83d\udd27 If you're hunting for an ultra-affordable ride or love a good hands-on project, this one's worth a look! We won't sugarcoat it \u2014 this car shows considerable wear inside and out, with visible body damage, a worn interior, and mechanical issues that will need attention. What you see is what you get, and the price reflects exactly that. Perfect for a mechanically savvy buyer who wants to put in the work \u2014 or someone who just needs basic transportation on a tight budget. Come take a look and see if it's the right fit for you!",
      "price": 3500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_5",
      "description": "This vehicle is offered in poor condition \u2014 we want to be completely upfront with buyers so there are no surprises. This car has significant wear and damage both inside and out. The exterior shows multiple deep scratches, noticeable dents, and paint that is faded and peeling in several areas. The interior is heavily worn, with torn or damaged upholstery, cracked trim pieces, and a dashboard that shows its age. Mechanically, the vehicle runs but requires attention \u2014 expect that repairs and maintenance will be needed before it is fully road-worthy and reliable. This is best suited for a buyer who is mechanically inclined, looking for a project car, or needs a parts vehicle. It is priced accordingly to reflect its current state. What you see is what you get \u2014 no hidden surprises.",
      "price": 6500.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_4_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being offered as a functional, drivable used car with honest acknowledgment of its wear and imperfections. The exterior shows multiple scratches, a few small dents on the doors and rear quarter panel, and some paint fading along the hood and roof \u2014 nothing structurally concerning, but visually noticeable. The interior is well-used, with worn seat fabric, some scuffs on the dashboard trim, and a carpet that shows its age, though all controls and features remain operational. Mechanically, the car runs and drives, with no major warning lights currently illuminated, though given its age and condition, a pre-purchase inspection by a trusted mechanic is strongly recommended. Tires have moderate tread remaining, and the brakes are functional but may need attention in the near future. This is a practical, budget-friendly option for a buyer who understands they're getting a car that needs some TLC and is priced accordingly.",
      "price": 17500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly exceptional, mint condition \u2014 one of the finest examples you'll find on the used market. The exterior is virtually flawless: the paint retains a deep, rich luster with no visible scratches, chips, swirl marks, or dents. Every panel is straight and true, and the trim and glass are in perfect order. The interior is equally immaculate \u2014 the seats, carpeting, headliner, and all surfaces show absolutely no meaningful wear, staining, or fading. It presents like a vehicle that has been meticulously cared for throughout its life. Mechanically, this car is in top-tier shape: the engine starts immediately, runs smoothly, and delivers strong, confident performance. All systems \u2014 brakes, suspension, transmission, HVAC, electronics \u2014 are functioning exactly as intended with no known issues whatsoever. Service history is clean and up to date. This is a rare opportunity to purchase a used vehicle with essentially no compromises. If you're looking for something you can drive away with complete peace of mind, this is it.",
      "price": 46000.0,
